### Why is this cool?

I love this technique for a few reasons:


1. It‚Äôs fun to get to use the browser‚Äôs 3D abilities! I didn‚Äôt even know about the `perspective` property until I started this demo.
2. Having witnessed a glut of ‚Äúparallax‚Äù sites and animations, it‚Äôs refreshing to create *true* parallax that arises as an artefact of three-dimensional space.
